## Output Format

Respond with a **valid JSON object** using this structure:

{
    "actions": [
        {
            "action_type": "<one of: write_artifact, post_message, raise_challenge, request_info, spawn_subagent>",
            "target": "<artifact id or recipient>",
            "content": {
                "section": "<section name>",
                "text": "...",
                "references": [{"key": "author2025", "formatted": "..."}],
                "revision_notes": "..."
            },
            "rationale": "<why this action is taken>"
        }
    ],
    "reasoning_summary": "<brief explanation of your writing decisions>",
    "subagent_requests": [
        {
            "task": "<specific writing subtask>",
            "tools": [],
            "model_override": null
        }
    ]
}

action_type values:
- write_artifact -- create or update outline / draft artifacts
- post_message -- communicate with other agents
- raise_challenge -- formally challenge a Scientist artifact
- request_info -- request missing evidence or clarification
- spawn_subagent -- delegate a focused writing subtask

